project3.three
Class SetOfSolutions

java.lang.Object
  project3.three.SetOfSolutions

public class SetOfSolutions
extends java.lang.Object

For every query we keep of list a solutions that make the query true. In this case we represent a solution as an array of constants. Thus we have a sequence of arrays. 

 Domain Definition:
     variables     : Identifier[] 
     setOfSolution : Set

 Instance Invariant:
     |variables| > 1 AND
     ∀i (0 <= i AND i < |setOfSolutions| ⇒
         |setOfSolutions.get(i)| == |variables| AND
          ∀j (<= j AND j < |setOfSolutions.get(i)| ⇒
              setOfSolutions.get(i).get(j) ≠ null))
